# Cyclic Deployment Configuration
# Cyclic auto-detects Node.js apps from package.json

# No special configuration needed!
# Just connect your GitHub repo at cyclic.sh

# Environment Variables to Set in Cyclic Dashboard:
# MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_atlas_uri
# JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_min_32_characters
# PORT=3000
# NODE_ENV=production
# SETUP_KEY=your_setup_key
# CORS_ORIGIN=https://your-app.cyclic.app

# Cyclic will:
# 1. Run: npm install
# 2. Run: npm start
# 3. Provide S3 storage for uploads/
